tip.text: Dunno what the hype is. Pretty rubbish.
The best Melbourne breakfast I've had is in Paris. You need to come to this place. Seriously. No excuses. Stop what you're doing right now - and come here.
Service was great. The French Onion Soup was pretty good too (although, I think I got an old batch, because my partners one was way tastier than mine)
Possibly the best breakfast I had in all of Scotland. All of it was super tasty. Definitely check it out.
